### BabyCare AI Server — API Tests
### VS Code REST Client (.http) — install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### Run: click "Send Request" above each ###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Health Check
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Register
### ────────────────────────────────────────
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Login  →  copy accessToken below
### ────────────────────────────────────────
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ── Set these after login ──────────────
@accessToken  = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Refresh Token
### ────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. Create Baby
### ────────────────────────────────────────
# @name createBaby
POST {{baseUrl}}/babies
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "小明",
  "nickname": "小明宝",
  "birthday": "2025-01-15",
  "gender": "男"
}

### ── Set after createBaby ───────────────
@babyId = PASTE_BABY_ID_HERE

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. List Babies
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/babies
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Update Baby
### ────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "小明",
  "nickname": "明明",
  "birthday": "2025-01-15",
  "gender": "男"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 8. Create Feeding Event
### ────────────────────────────────────────
# @name createEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "label": "feeding",
  "startTime": "2026-07-06T08:00:00Z",
  "payload": {
    "method": "formula",
    "amountMl": 120,
    "wasBurped": true,
    "hadSpitUp": false
  },
  "note": "喝得很好"
}

### ── Set after createEvent ──────────────
@eventId = PASTE_EVENT_ID_HERE

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 9. Create Sleep Event
### ────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "label": "sleep",
  "startTime": "2026-07-06T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-07-06T10:30:00Z",
  "payload": {
    "sleepType": "daytime",
    "quality": "good"
  }
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 10. List Events (with filters)
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events?from=2026-07-06T00:00:00Z&label=feeding
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 11. Incremental Sync
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events/sync?since=2026-07-05T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 12. Update Event
### ────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "label": "feeding",
  "startTime": "2026-07-06T08:05:00Z",
  "payload": {
    "method": "formula",
    "amountMl": 150
  },
  "note": "更新奶量"
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 13. Delete Event (soft delete)
### ────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 14. Create Growth Record
### ────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/growth
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "date": "2026-07-06",
  "weightKg": 6.5,
  "heightCm": 65.2,
  "headCm": 40.5
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 15. List Growth Records
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/growth
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 16. Upsert Growth (same day overwrites)
### ────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/babies/{{babyId}}/growth
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "date": "2026-07-06",
  "weightKg": 6.6,
  "heightCm": 65.3,
  "headCm": 40.6
}

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 17. 401 — No token (should fail)
### ────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/babies

### ────────────────────────────────────────
### 18. Delete Account (App Store requirement)
### ────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/auth/account
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
